T1  - On a Problem of Production Planning for a Non-Storable Commodity
AU  - Zaki, R. M.
AU  - Bhattacharyya, B. B.
AU  - Anderson, R. L.
Y1  - 1964/04/01
PY  - 1964
DA  - 1964/04/01
